{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Window.crypto","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/API/crypto_property","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/crypto_property\"><code>Crypto_property</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propriété, en lecture seule, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/crypto_property\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>Window.crypto</code></a> retourne l'objet <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Crypto\"><code>Crypto</code></a> associé à l'objet global. Cet objet permet aux pages web d'avoir un accès à certains services liés à cryptographie.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> cryptoObj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>crypto <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>msCrypto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// pour IE 11</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spécifications","title":"Spécifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Spécification</th>\n      <th>Statut</th>\n      <th>Commentaire</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/WebCryptoAPI/#dfn-GlobalCrypto\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Cryptography API<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'Window.crypto' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n      <td>Définition initiale</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.Window.crypto","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"voir_aussi","title":"Voir aussi","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>L'objet global <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li>\n  <li>L'interface <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Crypto\"><code>Crypto</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntaxe","id":"syntaxe"},{"text":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"},{"text":"Voir aussi","id":"voir_aussi"}],"summary":"La propriété, en lecture seule, Window.crypto retourne l'objet Crypto associé à l'objet global. Cet objet permet aux pages web d'avoir un accès à certains services liés à cryptographie.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"self.crypto","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.crypto","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"self.crypto","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.crypto","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"window.crypto","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Window.crypto","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.crypto","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.crypto","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/crypto_property","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/crypto_property/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API","title":"Référence Web API"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/crypto_property","title":"Window.crypto"}],"pageTitle":"Window.crypto - Référence Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}